### Ken Walker's GitHub

I'll try to keep this page up to date with any activity I have on my GitHub account.  This includes samples, examples and any [Orion Project](http://eclipse.org/orion) Plugins I write.

You can find me on twitter [@kwalker](http://twitter.com/kwalker).

**List of GitHub Projects**

* [Snippet Plugin for Orion](http://kenwalker.github.com/snippet/Snippet.html)
* [Double 2 Single Quotes plugin for Orion](http://kenwalker.github.com/Double2Single/Double2Single.html)
* [Mozilla Web App Example](https://github.com/kenwalker/webapp_example)
